    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Tourist is a chill, mechanic-lite space exploration game designed for those who love to discover beautiful worlds without overwhelming systems. An easy exploration game. Visit planets. Plant flags. Take photos. Relax. Are you a tired gamer looking for a mechanic-lite experience?  All that sound good? Space Tourist is a game made for you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/f46728bd282d7ac5b725ea1d4e7c10ff.poster.avif?t=1765890842\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/f46728bd282d7ac5b725ea1d4e7c10ff.webm?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/f46728bd282d7ac5b725ea1d4e7c10ff.mp4?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Overview:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Space Tourist, you step into the jetpack suit of a space explorer, venturing into uncharted nebulas and star systems to plant flags and take stunning photographs. The game is about easy exploration, perfect for unwinding. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/ddec236dfb2d20437f6895f9d3119b69.poster.avif?t=1765890842\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/ddec236dfb2d20437f6895f9d3119b69.webm?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/ddec236dfb2d20437f6895f9d3119b69.mp4?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expansive Universe: With 200 stars and over a thousand planets, there's always something new to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Planets: Each planet is distinct, offering diverse landscapes and stunning visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photo Journal: Create a personal collection of photographs that document your travels across the galaxy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flag Planting: Leave your mark on each planet by planting flags</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why Play Space Tourist?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Tourist is designed for those who appreciate the beauty of space. It's a  mechanic-lite experience, focusing on exploration and the joy of discovery. The scarcity of visits and limited photos ensure that each moment you spend in the game is meaningful and memorable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/891cd64707a7fa8f479cfdf252990f13.poster.avif?t=1765890842\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/891cd64707a7fa8f479cfdf252990f13.webm?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079270/extras/891cd64707a7fa8f479cfdf252990f13.mp4?t=1765890842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an adventure into the  wonder of space exploration!</p>",
